text: Only Bihari jisse UPSC dena is not allowed. Pura din phati rehne ka rr karega end mein sabse jyada chapega. Iss bande ke paas interview phodne ke liye gyan hai, chapuness hai, personality hai, charbi bhi hai bas agar nahi hai toh woh hai joota. Intern and placement ka party nahi diya koi nahi bas kabhi kabhi koi code doon toh bana dena.
